  "title": "A policeman saw a UFO going up and down in the sky of Alagoinhas [2015]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/05/30/a-policeman-spotted-a-ufo-rising-and-falling-in-the-sky-of-alagoinhas-2015/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-47",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 7th, 2015.</strong> Time: 20h30. The Salvador Approach Control (APP-SV) obtained the information that &#8220;a federal highway policeman had spotted an illuminated UFO going up and down in the sky over the city of Alagoinhas, State of Bahia, at around 20h30 pm&#8221;. According to the report by COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command] based on the information from the APP-SV, &#8220;after several attempts, there was no contact to obtain further details about the fact&#8221;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.728. &#8220;<span class=\"s1\" style=\"color:#808000;\"><span class=\"s1\"><i>Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni) em Alagoinhas, Bahia</i></span></span>&#8220;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
